     public void launchURL(String s)        {            String s1 = System.getProperty("os.name");            try            {                            if(s1.startsWith("Windows"))                {                    Runtime.getRuntime().exec((new StringBuilder()).append("rundll32 url.dll,FileProtocolHandler ").append(s).toString());                } else                {                    String as[] = {                        "firefox", "opera", "konqueror", "epiphany", "mozilla", "netscape"                    };                    String s2 = null;                    for(int i = 0; i < as.length && s2 == null; i++)                        if(Runtime.getRuntime().exec(new String[] {        "which", as[i]    }).waitFor() == 0)                            s2 = as[i];                    if(s2 == null)                        throw new Exception("Could not find web browser");                    Runtime.getRuntime().exec(new String[] {                        s2, s                    });                }            }            catch(Exception exception)            {                System.out.println("An error occured while trying to open the web browser!\n");            }        }
